data.title: Unofficial New York Codes, Rules and Regulations
data.text:
Welcome to the newly enhanced site for an unofficial version of New York Codes, Rules and Regulations (NYCRR). This site has been upgraded to ensure you a positive Thomson Reuters Westlaw Experience. This website is maintained by Thomson Reuters under contract with the New York State Department of State, which manages NYCRR.

If you cannot access a title due to high traffic on the site: please wait a few minutes, refresh your browser, and try again.

If you receive a message that your Weblinks session has timed out: delete your cookies, close your browser, and try again.

IMPORTANT NOTES REGARDING CONTENT CURRENCY:

In this unofficial version, the date provided at the end of each rule section indicates the date of the most recently produced official hardcopy NYCRR supplement that updated the official NYCRR Volume housing the section. Rule adoptions altering a section after such provided date, if any, have not been incorporated into this version.To determine whether a section has been altered by a rule adoption that may have occurred after such a date, please: consult editions of the NYS Register published after such provided date, or contact the NYS Department of State Division of Administrative Rules at [email protected].

Some portions of this unofficial version of NYCRR, which provides free electronic access to rules of New York State agencies, may be more current than other portions. This version is intended for informational purposes only. No representation is made as to the currency of this unofficial version, which should not be used for evidentiary or any other official purpose. For any such purpose, please consult: the official hardcopy NYCRR, which is available for purchase from Thomson Reuters, and pertinent editions of the NYS Register published after the date provided at the end of each rule section. Because such provided date indicates the most recently produced official hardcopy NYCRR supplement that updated the official NYCRR Volume housing the section, editions of the weekly NYS Register published after such date may contain subsequent rule adoptions that have altered the section.

By using this website, you agree not to use it in any manner that could disable, overburden, damage, or impair the site or interfere with any other partyâ€™s use of the website, or to use any device, software or routine that interferes with the proper working of the website.
